	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Actually, if you go to Layers-&gt;Colors-&gt;Colorcube Analysis, you can see the number of different colors in any image, whether the image is 8-bit or not. I just tested it with a photo that has about 25000 different colors. This is in version 2.2.10, so it may have been moved to a different menu in newer versions.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


