		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Dwedit wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Noah's ark appears to use the monochrome bit, possibly along with the color emphasis bits.</div>
<br />Yes, it does. The water is monochrome with blue emphasis. Not the most realistic water effect in the world, but the best you can do on the NES without messing with the palette itself, something that would be way more complicated to do during rendering.

		

